                <a class="w3-button button-color-inverse w3-text-white w3-border w3-round-xxlarge w3-small" style="font-weight:bolder" href="/redeem/10-off">redeem</a>
                <span class="w3-small">1000 points</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
<hr>
          <span style="cursor:pointer" onclick="myFunction('faq1')" class="w3-padding w3-block w3-left-align w3-border w3-round-large"><b>How do I earn points? <span class="w3-right"> <i class="fa fa-angle-down"></i> </b></span> </span>
